headline: Enlight Strengthens US Presence With New Financing Deals For Clean Energy Projects
summary: Enlight Renewable Energy (NASDAQ: ENLT) said its U.S. subsidiary, Clēnera Holdings, has finalized two tax equity partnerships for the Roadrunner Solar and Energy Storage Project near Tucson, Arizona. Morgan Chase Bank (NYSE: JPM) will provide financing for the 290-megawatt solar portion, while M&T Bank (NYSE: MTB) and First Citizens Bank (NASDAQ: FCNCA) are backing the 940-megawatt-hour storage facility.
